{"word":"παρατηρέω","slug":"παρατηρέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>παρατηρέω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:παρά\">παρά</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:τηρέω\">τηρέω</a></el>] ‘watch from the side’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> of surveillance <b>keep an eye on, keep close watch on, observe closely <a href='B:480 3:2'>Mk 3:2</a>; <a href='B:490 6:7'>Lk 6:7</a>; <a href='B:490 14:1'>14:1</a>; <a href='B:490 20:20'>20:20</a>; <a href='B:510 9:24'>Ac 9:24</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> of careful attention to cultic detail <b>observe <a href='B:550 4:10'>Gal 4:10</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:παρατείνω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:παρατήρησις\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}